Usage:  p7sign -k keyname [-d keydir] [-i input] [-o output]
-k keyname           Nickname of key to use for signature
-d keydir            Key database directory (default is ~/.netscape)
-i input             Define an input file to use (default is stdin)
-o output            Define an output file to use (default is stdout)
-e                   Encapsulate content in signature message
-p                   Password to the key databse
-f                   password file
